  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["y", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d2930d7e-c12f-4282-ad4d-2ac94f994b02"],
 "). Such an operation could be used, for example, to change the coordinate \
system. We can write out this transformation as"
}], "Text",
