   3.8113275877498016`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8289202a-d3e8-40bd-9580-\
d28e3e2ceebe"],

Cell["\<\
Sometimes this inner product is also called the scalar product of two \
vectors. It may also be written as\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8113234483101535`*^9, 3.811323491085661*^9}, {
  3.811323697390012*^9, 
